# Backend Kore (Go)

## Architecture module

```
internal/modules/{name}/
  domain/ ports/ app/ adapters/{http,postgres}/
```

## Auth

JWT `authx` — claims `sub`, `tenant_id`, `profile`. RBAC : `authorizer.Can(ctx, module, action)`.

## CRA statuts

`Brouillon`, `ValidéSemaine`, `Définitif` — mapper frontend via `useCraStatus`.

## Commandes

```bash
go build ./cmd/kore-api/
make migrate && make test
```
